ategy in the years to come.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aInternational Studies. 4aPolitical Science & Political History. 4aU.S. History.  aPresidential strategy, foreign policy, American leaders.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311060674440uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978080147028840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780801470288423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780801470288/original  a978-3-11-060674-4  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles